rows.label: tev020701_SEL0021
rows.name: Ask Grette if anything is troubling her.

rows.label: tev020701_MSG0001
rows.name:
Have you ever picked any of the fruits or flowers that
grow here on Mira?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev020701_MSG0002
rows.name:
Some of those collectibles were named by the first
BLADEs who discovered them.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev020701_MSG0003
rows.name:
I myself found a brilliant white feather once,
and gave it the name of "queen's rapture."
It was quite the thrilling experience![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev020701_MSG0004
rows.name:
I hope my dear friend Phina can experience that
incredible feeling one day![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev020701_MSG0008
rows.name: Our team will be heading out on an expedition shortly.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev020701_MSG0009
rows.name:
We'll set up a camp to use as a hub for a long-term
survey of the area, as well as the extermination of
dangerous indigens.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev020701_MSG0010
rows.name:
But I have no idea how I'm going to maintain proper
hygiene out there.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev020701_MSG0011
rows.name:
Perhaps I can convince my loyal manservant Adelbert
and his assistant Dirk to install a shower.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev020701_MSG0016
rows.name:
Indigens have been known to drop precious items
on occasion.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev020701_MSG0017
rows.name:
Those items can be sold for large amounts of money,
or used as materials for the creation of powerful
equipment.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev020701_MSG0018
rows.name:
Are you familiar with the monster known as a cinicula?
The splendid horn it sometimes drops is a famous
example of a rare material.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev020701_MSG0019
rows.name:
I've sold a lot of salvaged materials for a lot of money,
in hopes of one day opening a shop in the commercial
district with my friend, Phina.[ST:wait ]
